com.mojang.serialization

Class CompressorHolder

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.mojang.serialization.CompressorHolder
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Compressable, Keyable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    MapCodec, MapDecoder.Implementation, MapEncoder.Implementation

    public abstract class CompressorHolder
extends Object
implements Compressable
    Abstract base class for Compressable objects. This class provides a default implementation of the method compressor(DynamicOps).
    Implementation Note:
    This class internally caches KeyCompressor objects generated from different serialization forms.
